## Unreleased
### Added
- Added `links` objects per json:api specification
- Added configuration option for pagination

### Changed
- CibouletteId::build_id moved to CibouletteIdSelector::build
- Better performance when building documents and responses
- Changed how resource are built, using a new structure holding more options

## [0.1.4] - 2021-05-13
### Fixed
- Error when deserializing multiple 'id's in relationships objects

## [0.1.3] - 2021-05-13
### Added
- Support multiple `id`s when building table and when parsing requests. The `id` are comma separated
- Added 'one' key for O2M/M2O relationships

